_json.gridTitle: Good to know for anyone with health insurance!
_json.description: It finally happened. Tumblr leaked into my real life last night. Apparently I am suffering from body negativity and starting to show 'thin privilege' for making a healthy life choice. You see, I've finally decided that I want a better life, and started out on a journey to get healthy. Working out, eating well, making healthy life decisions. Those around me who are healthy root me on, those who aren't throw shade every chance they get. "You're changing. I don't like it." "Why are you no...
